{
  "info": {
    "name": "LMS Dev1 \u2014 Platform & Identity (38 APIs)",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for Dev 1 microservices.\n\n**Services:**\n- eureka-server (8761) \u2014 service discovery\n- api-gateway (8080) \u2014 single entry point\n- auth-service (8081) \u2014 12 APIs\n- user-service (8082) \u2014 14 APIs\n- admin-service (8094) \u2014 12 APIs\n\n**Seed credentials:**\n- Admin: admin@cloudnexus.com / Password123!\n- Mentor: arjan@cloudnexus.com / Password123!\n- Student: alex.chen@example.com / Password123!\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Start all services (see README)\n2. Run **Login (admin)** first \u2014 tokens auto-save to collection variables\n3. Test remaining requests in order\n\n**IMPORTANT \u2014 Postman setup:**\n1. Import `LMS-Dev1-Postman-Environment.json` from the same folder\n2. Top-right dropdown \u2192 select **LMS Dev1 \u2014 Local** (not 'No environment')\n3. Run **03 Login (admin)** first to save tokens\nService URLs are also hardcoded as localhost fallbacks.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
